{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"646","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"南部電廠升級 減碳量等同逾千座大安森林公園效益","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>最新更新：<span lang='EN-US'>2020/03/03 16:24</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E5%8D%97%E9%83%A8%E9%9B%BB%E5%BB%A0.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 488px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>台電<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>日表示，南部電廠環保升級計畫自<span lang='EN-US'>2015</span>年起啟動，氮氧化物排放年減超過<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>成，二氧化碳減排近<span lang='EN-US'>40</span>萬噸，等同逾千座大安森林公園的吸碳量效益。（圖取自台電網頁<span lang='EN-US'>taipower.com.tw/TC</span>）</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>（中央社記者蔡芃敏台北<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>日電）台電表示，自<span lang='EN-US'>2015</span>年起啟動的南部電廠環保升級計畫，包括電廠<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>部機組、共<span lang='EN-US'>7</span>台氣渦輪機已完成環保設備更新，氮氧化物排放年減超過<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>成，二氧化碳減排近<span lang='EN-US'>40</span>萬噸，等同逾千座大安森林公園的吸碳量效益。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>台電今天發布新聞稿指出，為了兼顧供電與環保，台電在<span lang='EN-US'>2015</span>年啟動南部電廠環保升級計畫，<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>部機組、共<span lang='EN-US'>7</span>台氣渦輪機，陸續完成機組熱元件升級更新。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>設備升級後，氮氧化物（<span lang='EN-US'>NOx</span>）排放年減超過<span lang='EN-US'>60%</span>，將近<span lang='EN-US'>1400</span>噸。二氧化碳排放年減近<span lang='EN-US'>40</span>萬噸，等同超過<span lang='EN-US'>1000</span>座大安森林公園的吸碳量。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>台電解釋，複循環機組分為前段氣渦輪機發電及後段熱回收鍋爐發電，透過燃燒天然氣，讓高溫、高壓的熱燃氣推動氣渦輪機葉片，再帶動發電機轉換成為電力。南部電廠更新承受熱燃氣相關元件，包含低氮氧化物燃燒器、氣渦輪機葉片等，提升燃燒效率後，即可降低排放，更可延長機組大修週期，全場每小時發電能力還能增加<span lang='EN-US'>8.47</span>萬瓩。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>南部電廠歷史悠久、成立於<span lang='EN-US'>1955</span>年，是國民政府來台後首座興建火力電廠，也是台電唯一在都市的電廠。南部電廠當時肩負南部穩定供電責任，走過重工業發展、設立全世界首個加工出口區及高科技園區轉型。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>台電說，原本興建<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>部燃煤機組與<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>部氣渦輪機組，不過，南部電廠自<span lang='EN-US'>1990</span>年代起，陸續更新為<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>部燃氣複循環發電機組，目前總裝置容量達<span lang='EN-US'>111.78</span>萬瓩，年發電量約<span lang='EN-US'>80</span>億度，等同高雄地區用電每<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>度就有<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>度來自這座電廠。（編輯：郭無患）<span lang='EN-US'>1090303</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202003030180.aspx</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-03-04","clk_count":"188"}},"__N_SSG":true}